11 An Act relating to the Oklahoma State University
Medical Authority; making appropriations; stating
12 purposes; providing an effective date; and declaring
an emergency.
13
14
15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. There is hereby appropriated to the Oklahoma State
17 University Medical Authority, from any monies not otherwise
18 appropriated from the Statewide Recovery Fund (497) of the State
19 Treasury, the sum of Sixteen Million Two Hundred Thousand Dollars
20 ($16,200,000.00) or so much thereof as may be necessary to address
21 gaps in the Human Performance Project. Such funds shall be utilized
22 in a manner consistent with the recommendations adopted by the Joint
23 Committee on Pandemic Relief Funding on April 15, 2026.
24
Req. No. 3956 Page 1

1 SECTION 2. There is hereby appropriated to the Oklahoma State
2 University Medical Authority, from any monies not otherwise
3 appropriated from the Statewide Recovery Fund (497) of the State
4 Treasury, the sum of Fourteen Million Dollars ($14,000,000.00) or so
5 much thereof as may be necessary to address gaps in the
6 pharmaceutical expansion program. Such funds shall be utilized in a
7 manner consistent with the recommendations adopted by the Joint
8 Committee on Pandemic Relief Funding on April 15, 2026.
9 SECTION 3. This act shall become effective July 1, 2026.
10 SECTION 4. It being immediately necessary for the preservation
11 of the public peace, health or safety, an emergency is hereby
12 declared to exist, by reason whereof this act shall take effect and
13 be in full force from and after its passage and approval.
